data.description:
Discover the charm of this beautifully updated two-story home in Pecan Grove, just a quick bike ride away from the allure of Lagoon Park. Indulge your love for golf by effortlessly driving your cart to the nearby Lagoon Park Golf Trail. For nature enthusiasts, the outdoor trails at Lagoon Park are within easy reach, inviting you to bike, jog, or walk amidst natural splendor.

Inside, the expansive living room takes center stage with a captivating masonry-framed fireplace and thoughtfully designed built-in shelving. The spacious dining room seamlessly connects to the living area, creating a perfect space for entertaining friends or enjoying a delightful meal with loved ones.

The convenience of the master bedroom and en suite on the main floor offers a retreat-like feel. Ascend upstairs to find two additional bedrooms and a second bath, providing privacy and space for the whole family. The large, fully fenced backyard beckons for outdoor gatherings, barbecues, children's play, and pet-friendly activities.

Don't let this opportunity slip away. Schedule a tour now and immerse yourself in the beauty of this home, both inside and out!
